barely init w/ busybox
======================

This branch is a project cut above barely_init. It features using busybox as
the initramfs.


Building
--------

Just run:
    
    make

The initramfs would be created in the build folder.


Running
-------

You can use it with qemu:

    qemu-system-x86_64 \
        -kernel $(KERNEL_DIR)/latest/arch/x86_64/boot/bzImage \
        -initrd build/initramfs \
        -nographic -append "console=ttyS0"
    
